Package: CoQR
Title: Joint Dynamic Models for the VaR and CoVaR
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Date: 2022-06-09
Authors@R: 
    c(person("Timo", "Dimitriadis", , "timo.dimi@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-8322-360X")),
    person("Yannick", "Hoga", , "Yannick.Hoga@vwl.uni-due.de", role = c("aut")))
Description: The package estimates joint dynamic autoregressive or cross-sectional models of the VaR (Value-at-Risk) (i.e., the quantile) and the CoVaR of a bivariate vector of financial returns.
